## 🚀 **Quick Start Checklist**

### **Setting Up Development Environment**
```bash
# 1. Clone and install
git clone <repo-url>
cd infraFlux
npm install

# 2. Configure environment
cp env.example .env
# Edit .env with your Proxmox credentials

# 3. Validate configuration
npm run validate-config

# 4. Build and deploy
npm run build
pulumi stack init <stack-name>
pulumi up
```

### **Key File Locations**
- **Main Entry**: [src/index.ts](mdc:src/index.ts)
- **Configuration**: [src/config/index.ts](mdc:src/config/index.ts) + [env.example](mdc:env.example)
- **Components**: [src/components/](mdc:src/components)
